Complete Roguelike Tutorial, using Rust + tcod

This is a port of the infamous Python+libtcod tutorial:

http://www.roguebasin.com/index.php?title=Complete_Roguelike_Tutorial,_using_python%2Blibtcod


Parts 1 to 11 are implemented, parts 12 and 13 remain. The code is not split
into parts yet, that'll happen we've covered everything from the original
tutorial.

The tutorial text doesn't exist yet either. Again, we'll do that only after the
code is all ready.